          "label": "Git Synchronization",
          "startSec": 14.1125,
          "endSec": 28.0625,
          "text": "Git synchronization is the core idea: use Git as the bus for Kanban boards. Board updates become normal file changes, so review, history, branching, and collaboration work exactly the way your engineering team already expects.",
